<<twn buy pub>>=
        ORG $9655
BUY_PUB
        SUBROUTINE
        ; The Pub: buy a drink, risk seduction, or hear a rumour.
        ;
        ; Behavior:
        ;   One gold buys "a cold one".  Distance/charisma (NPC_DIST) gates
        ;   a seduction that halves the purse; otherwise a 75/256 roll
        ;   prints one of eight rumours from PUB_HINT_TBL (self-modified
        ;   JSR).  The rumours are the canonical Ultima I quest hints.
        LDA PLR_COIN
        ORA PLR_COIN+1
        BNE .L96AB
        JSR MSG_PRINT
        DC.B $7F,$07,"Thou art broke!~~",$7F,$03,"Come back when thou hast~",$7F,$05,"some money to spend.",0
        JSR PAUSE_ABORTABLE
        JMP SHOP_NOTHING_A
.L96AB
        DEC PLR_COIN
        LDA PLR_COIN
        CMP #$FF
        BNE .L96B8
        DEC PLR_COIN+1
.L96B8
        JSR MSG_PRINT
        DC.B "~",$7F,$02,"The tavern keeper sayeth:~~",$7F,$03,"Here, have a cold one!",0
        JSR WIN_SAVE
        JSR WIN_TEXT
        LDY #$17
        LDX #$0F
        JSR MSG_AT
        DC.B "ale",0
        JSR WIN_RESTORE
        JSR PAUSE_ABORTABLE
        JSR CLEAR_MSGS
        LDA #$08
        STA MON_CV
        INC PUB_VISITS
        LDA PLR_STA
        LSR
        LSR
        CMP PUB_VISITS
        BEQ .L971F
        BCS PUB_HINT
.L971F
        LDX #$01
        JSR NPC_DIST
        CMP #$02
        BCS PUB_HINT
        JSR MSG_PRINT
        DC.B $7F,$03,"Thou hast been seduced!~~",$7F,$05,"After a long night,~",$7F,$07,"thou art back.",0
        LSR PLR_COIN+1
        ROR PLR_COIN
        DEC PLR_WIS
        LDA PLR_WIS
        CMP #$05
        BCS .L9782
        LDA #$05
        STA PLR_WIS
.L9782
        JMP PAUSE_ABORTABLE
PUB_HINT
        JSR RND
        CMP #$4B
        BCS .L978D
        RTS
.L978D
        JSR MSG_PRINT
        DC.B $7F,$06,"Thou had best know~",0
        JSR RND
        LSR
        LSR
        LSR
        LSR
        LSR
        ASL
        TAX
        LDA PUB_HINT_TBL,X
        STA HINT_OP
        LDA PUB_HINT_TBL+1,X
        STA HINT_OP+1
HINT_OP = *+1
        JSR STALE_FFFF
        JMP PAUSE_ABORTABLE
@

Each rumour is a short routine that prints its inline text and
returns; [[PUB_HINT_TBL]] (in the data appendix) selects one at random.
Together they are the game's built-in walkthrough --- the ace pilot
goal, the captive princess, the time machine, and the truth about
Mondain's gem.

<<twn pub hints>>=
        ORG $97C2
HINT_SPACE
        SUBROUTINE
        ; The eight tavern rumours.  Each prints its own inline text
        ; and returns; PUB_HINT_TBL selects one at random and reaches
        ; it through a self-modified JSR.
        ;
        ; Behavior:
        ;   Print the hint, RTS.  These are the game's quest hints:
        ;   the ace-pilot goal, the jester, the captive princess, the
        ;   time machine, the evil gem, magic lakes, and Mondain.
        JSR MSG_PRINT
        DC.B $7F,$05,"about space travel!~",$7F,$05,"Thou must destroy at~",$7F,$04,"least 20 enemy vessels~",$7F,$06,"to become an ace!",0
        RTS
