        ORG $9E01
SHOP_DEBIT
        SUBROUTINE
        ; Shared shop utilities: debit, affordability, key input, the
        ; "Sold!"/"Done!"/"too poor" messages, and the price calculators.
        ;
        ; Behavior:
        ;   PRICE_MUL forms PRICE = base * factor by repeated addition;
        ;   the factor derives from PLR_CHA/PLR_WIS/PLR_INT so a charismatic
        ;   buyer pays less and sells for more.
        LDA PLR_COIN
        SEC
        SBC PRICE
        STA PLR_COIN
        LDA PLR_COIN+1
        SBC PRICE+1
        STA PLR_COIN+1
        JMP SHOP_SOLD
SHOP_CANAFFORD
        LDA PLR_COIN
        CMP PRICE
        LDA PLR_COIN+1
        SBC PRICE+1
        RTS
