\subsection{Cast (disabled)}

As in town, magic does nothing useful in a castle: [[CMD_CAST]] just
prints ``no effect?'' and beeps.

<<cas cast>>=
        ORG $8E3C
CMD_CAST
        SUBROUTINE
        ; Cast: spells have no effect inside a castle.
        ;
        ; Behavior:
        ;   Print "no effect?" and beep.  (Magic is an overworld/dungeon
        ;   command; the castle disables it the same way the town does.)
        ;
        ; Clobbers: A
        JSR MSG_PRINT
        DC.B "-- Hmmmm... no effect?",0
