        ;
        ; Behavior:
        ;   Require the King in the faced cell and no standing grudge
        ;   (KING_REJECT clear).  If this castle's quest flag is already
        ;   "completed" (high bit set), go to QUEST_COMPLETE.  Otherwise
        ;   offer "pence or service": P runs KING_PENCE (gold for HP at
        ;   1.5x), S runs QUEST_ASSIGN.
