\subsection{Quest assignment}

Asking for service runs [[QUEST_ASSIGN]]. If a quest for this castle
is already open it refuses (``thou art on a quest for me already''),
otherwise it sets the flag and chooses a quest by the castle's
parity. An \emph{even} castle sends the player to \emph{find} a
place, named from [[STR_PLACES]] by a small continent calculation; an
\emph{odd} castle ([[QUEST_KILL]]) sends the player to \emph{kill} a
monster, named from [[STR_MONSTERS]] at index $5c + \$1E$ where $c$
is the continent [[PLR_CONT]]. [[CASTLE_COL]] supplies the text column
so the name lands neatly in the King's speech.

<<cas quest assign>>=
        ORG $93FB
QUEST_ASSIGN
        SUBROUTINE
        ; Assign a quest (even castle: find a place; odd: kill a monster).
        ;
        ; Behavior:
        ;   Refuse a second quest while one is open.  Mark the flag, then by
        ;   castle parity name the target: EVEN -> "find" a place from
        ;   STR_PLACES (continent math), ODD -> "kill" a monster from
        ;   STR_MONSTERS (PLR_CONT*5 + $1E).  CASTLE_COL sets the print
        ;   column.
        ;
        ; Clobbers: A, X, Y
        JSR MSG_PRINT
        DC.B "service",0
        LDX CASTLE_IDX
        LDA QUEST_FLAGS,X
        BEQ .L9437
        JSR MSG_PRINT
        DC.B "~Thou art on a quest~for me already!",0
        RTS
.L9437
        INC QUEST_FLAGS,X
        JSR POPUP_FRAME
        LDX #$07
        LDY #$07
        LDA CASTLE_IDX
        LSR
        BCS QUEST_KILL
        JSR MSG_AT
        DC.B "Go forth and find||",0
        LDX CASTLE_IDX
        LDA CASTLE_COL,X
        STA MON_CH
        LDA #$03
        SEC
        SBC PLR_CONT
        TAX
        LDA #$02
.L946F
        DEX
        BMI .L9478
        CLC
        ADC #$15
        JMP .L946F
.L9478
        TAX
        JSR STR_NTH
        DC.W STR_PLACES
.L947E
        JSR MSG_PRINT
        DC.B "||",$7F,$06,"Do not return until|",$7F,$06,"thy quest is done!",0
        JSR CLEAR_MSGS
        JMP MAP_DRAW
QUEST_KILL
        JSR MSG_AT
        DC.B "Go now and kill a||",0
        LDX CASTLE_IDX
        LDA CASTLE_COL,X
        STA MON_CH
