        ;
        ; Behavior:
        ;   Print a prophecy and grant the matching gem in OWNED_GEMS:
        ;   red (all four gems launch the machine), green (the machine
        ;   must be used to win), blue (the princess helps a space ace),
        ;   white (take nine items from storerooms -> STORE_PERMIT := 9).
