The monster, chest and ladder-cell figures, as line drawings.
Each of the 25 shapes (rendered in
\verb|images/dng_monster_shapes.png|) is a polyline: a list of
\((x,y,\text{flag})\) triples where \((x,y)\) is a vertex
relative to the screen-centre origin and the flag chooses move
(pen up) versus draw. [[SHAPE_DRAW]] scales every vertex down by
the view depth so the figure shrinks into the distance.

